Class Description
AbstractLetterFactory
An abstract factory pattern applied to generating words in different alphabets.
Chromosome<Letter>
This class represents a geneticAlgorithm.Chromosome object where it holds the value of the words, the fitness score, and a flag for recalculation purposes.
CrossOverStrategy
This class represents the crossover strategy where two population changes chromosomes between them to improve success rate.
EnglishLetterFactory
A factory class to create Letter objects in English alphabet
GeneticAlgorithm
Represent the geneticAlgorithm.GeneticAlgorithm class where it demonstrates the basic structure of a genetic algorithm with mutation, crossover and evolution.
LanguageFactory  
Letter
Represents a Letter class where a Letter has a char value.
Main
This class in the runner of the application.
MutationStrategy
This class represents the idea of Mutation on Genetic Algorithm, where some of the chromosomes randomly changes.
Parameters
This class is to store the parameters that are used in genetic algorithm
Population
A class represents a geneticAlgorithm.Population, where a population consists of a collection of chromosomes.
RussianLetterFactory
A factory class to create Letter objects in English alphabet
SelectionStrategy
This class is to select the possible candidates for our genetic algorithm. each of the population member will be sorted based on their fitness scores.
StrategyInterface
An interface for making strategy methods controlled from one place.
